title: Changelings Series by Michele Hauf
description:
01 Seraphim

In a land where the battle between Good and Evil is always near, one Knight will make the cruel brotherhood pay for the region of terror they have caused and along the way uncover the power she holds within.

02 Gossamyr

But this is Gossamyr's first trip to the war-ravaged mortal realm, and it seduces with its own enchantments. With her new traveling companion, Gossamyr takes the first steps to save her people.
- Michele Hauf is the author of over eight romance novels. Gossamyr is her second fantasy novel.
- Gossamyr is the second book in a trilogy that takes place in an altered version of sixteenth-century France.

03 Rhiana

In this final book of Hauf's trilogy begun in "Seraphim" and "Gossamyr," Rhiana Tassot is stunned that the local lord forbids her to fight the dragons that have invaded her village. But she soon discovers a secret about her connection to them.
